<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Jakob von Wolfstein</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Freilassung des Hans Beheim, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_137" id="68r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_137_r1l30"><expan>Jacob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vom wolfſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_137_r1l31">Lıeber Jacob / vns 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan></del> hat fürgelegt Hans Beheim <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l32">vvie daʒ Jr Jn gefangen habt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jn ledig laſſen wollet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l33">das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / vnd het Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan> icht <expan>cʒeſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l34"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew / oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_137" id="68r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Jacob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vom Wolfstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Jacob, uns hat fürgelegt Hans Beheim, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz ir in gefangen habt.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in ledig lassen wollet, das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan> icht <expan>cze spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
